Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.69,0:02:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.10,0:02:36.07,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『每一天。』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浑身乏力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.93,0:02:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是喝得烂醉而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.00,0:02:44.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上自己的房间里去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:48.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4}23       24\N纪念日   休息\N休息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.58,0:02:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天开始就是长假了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱家有没有出行预定什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.41,0:02:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出去玩啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得的休假日蜷在家里不觉得悲哀么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.35,0:03:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正对姐姐来说和平时也没什么不同吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.29,0:03:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先你拿这事情来缠着我也没用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.30,0:03:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「反正长假什么的和我没关系」是么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.42,0:03:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千你这一副cool相不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.60,0:03:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假期我也是想出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？终于说出心里话了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.73,0:03:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要喝么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上的同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.48,0:03:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的都全家一起去夏威夷度假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:26.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么「真好啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.12,0:03:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真想去夏威夷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是在地球的另一侧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一片的冰天雪地哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.45,0:03:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别瞎扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹夏威夷我还是知道一些的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.64,0:03:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别为点小事就这么认真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:38.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你也去不成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长假嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划是在家里过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为安娜会出门去度假呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前你不是去英格兰了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.32,0:03:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由堂兄弟们带路环游伦敦城什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:03:57.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.29,0:03:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,语言也不通
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好累人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些不列颠的小家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次非得把你们晾在巢鸭的刺拔地藏大道上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:08.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：东京都丰岛区巢鸭地方的高严寺之俗称）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你们晃悠个够
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不让你们十倍地偿还我可咽不下这口气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事情么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉…茉莉在长假有什么打算？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:25.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假里说好上爷爷家里去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可现在才刚开春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.50,0:04:33.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以得从现在开始就储备体力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长假就不出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎样的体力啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.53,0:04:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是动物的冬眠一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是茉莉所以我许可了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里都好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想出去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么着使性子做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是小孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这丫头做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不都因为姐姐你提起这个事情来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神来啊  小千
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:04.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看我出行预定和零花钱都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不活得挺滋润么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来尝点这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:10.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.40,0:05:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:13.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么  你不想要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说那是我做的蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:24.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  怎么一直这么使性子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你在边上火上浇油的么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么该拿出那玩意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个玩意？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:31.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得是在这附近…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:38.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:40.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你个头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.26,0:05:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国民宿舍伊豆风情之旅招待券
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  这是哪儿弄来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.50,0:05:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正月的时候中了超市的抽彩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么兴趣就忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:05:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是国民宿舍？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参与健康保险的人可以低开销利用的公共设施
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.93,0:06:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～是说Health Hostel？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以这么叫吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:11.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  去吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.21,0:06:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  吊人家的胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸惠姐白痴弱智二百五
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:21.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来就没有出游预定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.58,0:06:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千佳很是寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:24.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.62,0:06:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换作我可能都要哭出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听啊听啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家在同情你哦  小千
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  不是那么一回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.54,0:06:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是和小千两个人去也很无聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  我加入你们！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸惠姐白痴弱智二百五
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.47,0:06:43.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  倒是配合得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.26,0:06:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:45.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平胸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又上套了  小千
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.41,0:06:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话我也想去…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:06:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:06:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.09,0:07:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且对茉莉来说也是个积攒体力的好方法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都想去么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.14,0:07:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:12.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.44,0:07:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过可不是什么稀奇地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跟来了又一肚子的牢骚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:20.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出游喽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊豆是个怎样的地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:25.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…伊豆啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吊桥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.91,0:07:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经在照片上看过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桥底下有喜欢香蕉的鳄鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在保护着它们的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到伊豆的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.38,0:07:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以舞女而出名的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞女？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:48.14,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（伊豆之舞女）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:02.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（临时新闻  [致歉]由于插播插播新闻  电影的播放无限制延期）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在插播临时新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.89,0:08:07.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到伊豆  伊豆的舞女  香蕉是很有名的…鳄鱼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的…舞女…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.69,0:08:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滨松地区  降水概率20%
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是伊豆地区
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从午夜到清晨多云转晴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天为晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必担心云雨天气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位预定出游的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来是…天气预报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:41.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（给我放晴）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:58.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个晴天真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是晴天娃娃的功劳呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.01,0:09:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是大家一起做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.11,0:09:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你来指挥一下我把车开出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.06,0:09:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  现在Tail Slide
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后Spin Horn
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  没有落什么东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:28.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们就上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出游了呀嗬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.42,0:09:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀嗬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落东西了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:09:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.25,0:10:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人心情舒畅的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.68,0:10:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有令人心情舒畅的音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:05.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.53,0:10:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有别的CD了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:11.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到兜风的话不一直是放这种曲子的么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.49,0:10:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到伊豆还得多远？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.49,0:10:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？差不多还20公里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.63,0:10:24.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:27.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来唱唱歌活跃气氛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:32.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么request么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「森林中的小熊」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.68,0:10:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「森林中的石松」也可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我没有那种CD…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.00,0:10:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前几天你买的那张呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:44.29,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（东京-静冈高速公路  新横滨）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是吉他之类好听的那张…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:49.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（八个小时后）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:54.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飚…飚车后一支烟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.53,0:11:03.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是赛过活神仙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.92,0:11:10.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你待在那种地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒是早说路上得八个小时啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不迷路的话俩小时就成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然迷路了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不没法子么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车上又没有装GPS…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:24.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来厕所在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…住宿…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这果实和在植物图鉴上看过的不一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯　比照片要漂亮好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.30,0:11:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上屋子里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:54.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千  把那边的报纸递给我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.15,0:12:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  赶上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.72,0:12:11.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漏了一点出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.65,0:12:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不许放我家的洗衣机里去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:26.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵  是一直都那么精神的喵喵啊喵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:28.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这副德行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平时待家里根本就没有区别嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不都说了么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近收不到爆笑静冈的节目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊  收视频道完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「完熟欲滴的少妇」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很新鲜嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:47.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（此节目为付费节目  若欲观看  请来前台办理）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？还要钱的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.47,0:12:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为谁会看这节目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:51.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（大浴池  本馆一层    馆内介绍）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:50.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这电视台真扯呢  大姐头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  浴室在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:53.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安娜  茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.95,0:12:55.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大浴池  好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  千佳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.18,0:13:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉莉  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  这浴池
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.59,0:13:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  不行啊  都一览无余了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也太大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连外面都能看进来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:21.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:24.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面看不见的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就是放不下心来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为你们把风
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人都下定决心把毛巾摘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下是真的一览无余了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:42.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？这里是温泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看写的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:44.99,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对更年期综合症\N不孕亦有疗效\N水质  二氧化碳…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:46.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了啊  茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:49.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来明天开始你就是未婚妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡个温泉就会怀上孩子不就太糟了么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:57.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说…说的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉莉你还真信了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  婴儿是怎么来的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.33,0:14:08.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这么突然…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…婴儿啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鹳衔来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐满脸通红～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么这么认…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.95,0:14:22.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你敢耍大人玩儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.77,0:14:24.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这丫头…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水都弄到脸上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉莉  都到浴池来了可得习惯水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.37,0:14:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  开始特训
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？等…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就给我沉在水里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小美真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在浴池里放屁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是安娜干的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:47.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是安娜干的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:52.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（明日天气）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日全天晴好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实为出行的绝好天气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:55.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  在一段广告之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:58.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请接着关注我们的天气预报
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么非得绕个弯儿来呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:05.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天的习惯还是很重要的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着美羽从窗户里进来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.06,0:15:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一时间都以为和平常一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把旅行的欢愉全都搅黄了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭是什么时候开始呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定不会规定什么用餐时间的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.86,0:15:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是让自己做饭  厨房可以随便用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  让自己做饭的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.42,0:15:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么食材呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:31.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘记了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.56,0:15:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  那晚饭怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节…节～食～？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:43.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  去还不成么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得住回旅馆居然吃速食？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是在家吃不上的美味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.89,0:16:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不大想吃这玩意儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过看上去真的很好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千佳做的什么都会变得好吃  真是不可思议呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.17,0:16:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.43,0:16:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  吃什么都成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点上桌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:28.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  吃得好饱好饱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:29.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还凑合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓是个人好歹就会有优点的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让谁收拾呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？好麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.71,0:16:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别小看她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.85,0:16:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千不但有一手好厨艺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:42.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收拾碗筷也是拿手好戏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是家好使唤人的黑店呢  大姐头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It cames to the…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…国民宿舍…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inexpensive hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.11,0:16:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:17:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I like some of Riceball
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Riceball？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  饭团
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.11,0:17:06.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐地能比较流畅地交流了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然现在肚子也吃得圆圆的了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.53,0:17:18.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来玩百物语吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:20.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：百物语，众人坐在一起讲鬼故事啊什么的…）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.24,0:17:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要说很可怕的故事么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.25,0:17:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看茉莉不是很害怕么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不玩不玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说姐姐你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:37.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太娇惯的话对茉莉的将来是没有好处的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:40.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那玩百物语对将来就有好处了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:43.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被硬扯去公司的酒会作陪的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.01,0:17:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是参事会议上没有话题了什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.91,0:17:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是个什么样的将来啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道什么是百物语…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.47,0:17:54.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就像接龙那样把故事续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后最后一个来结尾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:18:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒觉得从这一刻开始你就大错特错了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.13,0:18:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就从我开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在自己家睡着～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒来时却发现～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.08,0:18:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.56,0:18:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面安娜继续说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我说…么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.13,0:18:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想着怎么接着我刚才的说下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:20.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要恐怖的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐…恐怖的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明…明文堂的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:27.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：可参见OVA01中大伙儿买零食的店的店名）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:28.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爷爷…俳句…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…正站着…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.43,0:18:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在读…俳句？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  觉得不够味儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.17,0:18:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个小千你来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说得够味儿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.01,0:18:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俳句？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为是俳句的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.95,0:18:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不想那词句不合韵律
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:57.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：安娜之前所说的从结构上来说应为俳句(5-7-5)，\N而根据千佳的观点，可能第二句处多了字，所以知道不是俳句）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:19:00.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是一封信件
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:02.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可有点可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉…觉得听自己这么一说都有点毛骨悚然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来这故事是个什么玩意啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想发展成什么样的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  下一个是伸惠姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大吃一惊醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:21.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么觉得你是图省事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么最后是茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.09,0:19:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后你可得整个吓死人的结局哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.71,0:19:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓…吓死人的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.66,0:19:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:36.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒…醒来居然发现…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尿床了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不成？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.28,0:19:50.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  就到这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.99,0:19:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么结局到底是怎么样的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.37,0:19:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个真是闲得慌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千和安娜上那边睡去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么做太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  小美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好用猜拳来决定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:18.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡伸惠姐边上的应该是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不决定可就睡不成了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜负已分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:32.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就来猜拳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.18,0:20:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太…太狡猾了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茉莉  睡不着么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都先睡了就觉得很孤单呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着之前我一直陪着你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.46,0:21:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:15.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  要是有小偷来了怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把他收拾得七零八落的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.02,0:21:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以握着手睡么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.50,0:21:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.25,0:21:32.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有色狼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:41.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：其实美羽说的本是“{\fnzhunyuan\fs24}夜這{\r}”，意指溜进女人房里企图苟且的男子）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.47,0:21:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.45,0:21:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.47,0:21:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事情了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.14,0:21:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏哪儿去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.46,0:21:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我逮着了不把你做成佐竹的食粮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.65,0:21:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.22,0:21:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为佐竹食粮的会是谁呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.74,0:21:54.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.47,0:21:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成真的把手…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.64,0:22:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  姐姐她一定不是这个意思的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次别再说什么可爱之类的话了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.83,0:22:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢…蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.79,0:22:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别瞎想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.90,0:22:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.62,0:22:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这花心贼！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.58,0:22:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不放开茉莉我就这么着…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.74,0:22:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.21,0:22:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.28,0:22:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这变态！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不只是这样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.00,0:22:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认命吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.86,0:22:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你别太得意了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.01,0:22:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.47,0:22:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我才…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.29,0:22:42.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.17,0:22:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你平日里老做那样的事情才会被误会的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.87,0:22:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.56,0:22:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪儿误会了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.93,0:23:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.96,0:23:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.67,0:23:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从身边吹过的风
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.18,0:23:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从身边吹过？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.05,0:23:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  咦？这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.25,0:23:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风本来就是透明的  看不见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.25,0:23:18.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：日语中“透き通る”同时有“清澈”和“吹过”的意思）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.21,0:23:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有点奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.84,0:23:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.95,0:23:25.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.52,0:23:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时风吹过的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.73,0:23:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些平时的景色都突然换上了一身不同的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有这种事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.46,0:23:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是在同一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.98,0:23:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时候也会觉得「啊  今天和平时是不一样的颜色」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:44.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不可思议吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.88,0:23:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.33,0:23:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景色本身是没有色彩的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.83,0:23:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们感觉到的  只是自己那不同的心境
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到早上就得回去了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.64,0:24:11.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.10,0:24:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实开心的事情啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.00,0:24:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.20,0:24:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许就在我们习以为常的景色中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.72,0:24:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏着那许许多多
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.02,0:24:25.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说我们平时注意不到它们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.53,0:24:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.82,0:24:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要风儿吹过
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.57,0:24:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼前便能浮现出它们的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.45,0:24:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太假了～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.24,0:24:40.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美妙了  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.33,0:24:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怎么怎么  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.78,0:24:44.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.54,0:24:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸惠姐说了不像是她会说的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.17,0:24:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.23,0:24:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么也没说
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.02,0:24:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  是小孩子该睡觉的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.50,0:24:55.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.04,0:24:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.25,0:24:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再同大伙一起来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.34,0:25:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.64,0:25:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛  再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.61,0:25:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.71,0:25:43.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（大宫  15km  减速慢行  不急不躁地驾驶）
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.49,0:25:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.55,0:25:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又迷路了吧
